type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

A generalization of a [[Probability measure]] obtained by relaxing the additivity requirement to super-additivity, i.e. $$\mu(A\cup B) \geq \mu(A)  + \mu(B)$$, where $$A$$ and $$B$$ are disjoint events.

[[Randomness and Semi-measures|https://arxiv.org/abs/1310.5133]]